name: The Stranded
overview: Trapped on an island destroyed by a tsunami, the students of an elite school try to hold on to hope. But mysterious forces seem to work against them.
tagline: No one will be stranded alone

episodes.name: The Ruins
episodes.overview: The Ruins Privileged students party and prepare to part ways when a powerful tsunami slams into their island. Weeks later, hope of a rescue starts to slip away.

episodes.name: The Return
episodes.overview: Shaken, Kraam awakens from a bizarre dream. Anan struggles to lead as the students work to retrieve the boat. Meanwhile, Arisa makes a discovery.

episodes.name: The Code
episodes.overview: Nahm questions the mysterious appearance of Professor Lin, while Arisa and Ying try to piece together the puzzle of the poem. The past haunts Ice.

episodes.name: The Fall
episodes.overview: Professor Lin acts strangely, and Ice seeks an exorcism. Kraam sketches May and draws her to a special spot. Arisa makes contact deep in the jungle.

episodes.name: The Mutiny
episodes.overview: May thinks back on her life while Anan harbors suspicions. Lin warns of danger as the students get ready to set sail. Ying and Nahm hunt for answers.

episodes.name: The Attack
episodes.overview: As Krit’s captivity wears on, Lin delivers a cryptic message to Kraam. May makes a life-changing discovery. The jungle's mysteries pull Arisa deeper.

episodes.name: The Gate
episodes.overview: Panic grips the students in the aftermath of the chaotic launch, and Anan takes control of the mob. Kraam must be courageous enough to face the truth.
